= 3. <One time operation name> =

{{info}}If the project has some part of one time operations that need to be done which is unrelated to the application itself and potentially optional, such as data import from an excel, or a csv, for example (which will be valid for the first version of the project), you can put the instructions about how to perform these operations here.{{/info}}
